Name: REEF_NAME
Description: The name of the specific reef within a survey site

Name: REEF_ID
Description: Unique number code for each reef

Name: LATITUDE
Description: Latitude of each reef within a specific site

Name: LONGITUDE
Description: Longitude of each reef within a specific site

Name: P_CODE
Description: Denotes which program collected the data

Name: VISIT_NO
Description: The number of years the reef has been visited

Name: YEAR_CODE
Description: Indicates years that the survey was conducted

Name: REPORT_YEAR
Description: Indicates when the report for that site was issued

Name: SAMPLE_DATE
Description: Indicate the date the survey occurred

Name: TOTAL_COTS
Description: Total number of crown of thorn starfish seen on the survey

Name: MEAN_COTS_PER_TOW
Description: Average number of crown of thorn starfish seen on each tow within the survey

Name: TOTAL_TROUT
Description: Total number of coral trout seen on the survey

Name: MEAN_TROUT_PER_TOW
Description: Average number of coral trout seen on each tow within the survey

Name: TOWS
Description: Number of two minute survey tows completed on the reef on the sample date
